import "./BottomSection.css";
import QandA from "../QandA/QandA";
import { useState } from "react";
import Modal from "react-bootstrap/Modal";
import Tips from "../Tips/Tips";

const BottomSection = () => {
  const [show1, setShow1] = useState(false);
  const [show2, setShow2] = useState(false);
  const [show3, setShow3] = useState(false);
  const [show4, setShow4] = useState(false);
  const [show5, setShow5] = useState(false);
  const [show6, setShow6] = useState(false);

  return (
    <>
      <button className="modalButton" onClick={() => setShow1(true)}>
        Q and A
      </button>

      <button className="modalButton" onClick={() => setShow2(true)}>
        Tips
      </button>

      <button className="modalButton" onClick={() => setShow3(true)}>
        Global uppvärmning
      </button>

      <button className="modalButton" onClick={() => setShow4(true)}>
        Stigande havsnivåer
      </button>

      <button className="modalButton" onClick={() => setShow5(true)}>
        CO2-utsläpp
      </button>

      <button className="modalButton" onClick={() => setShow6(true)}>
        Smältande glaciärer
      </button>

      <Modal
        show={show1}
        onHide={() => setShow1(false)}
        dialogClassName="modal-90w"
        aria-labelledby="example-custom-modal-styling-title"
        className="modal"
      >
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title id="example-custom-modal-styling-title">
            Q and A
          </Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
          <QandA />
        </Modal.Body>
      </Modal>

      <Modal
        show={show2}
        onHide={() => setShow2(false)}
        dialogClassName="modal-90w"
        aria-labelledby="example-custom-modal-styling-title"
        className="modal"
      >
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title id="example-custom-modal-styling-title">
            Tips
          </Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
          <Tips />
        </Modal.Body>
      </Modal>

      <Modal
        show={show3}
        onHide={() => setShow3(false)}
        dialogClassName="modal-90w"
        aria-labelledby="example-custom-modal-styling-title"
      >
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title id="example-custom-modal-styling-title">
            Tips
          </Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
          <Tips />
        </Modal.Body>
      </Modal>

      <Modal
        show={show4}
        onHide={() => setShow4(false)}
        dialogClassName="modal-90w"
        aria-labelledby="example-custom-modal-styling-title"
      >
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title id="example-custom-modal-styling-title">
            Tips
          </Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
          <Tips />
        </Modal.Body>
      </Modal>

      
      <Modal
        show={show5}
        onHide={() => setShow5(false)}
        dialogClassName="modal-90w"
        aria-labelledby="example-custom-modal-styling-title"
      >
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title id="example-custom-modal-styling-title">
            Tips
          </Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
          <Tips />
        </Modal.Body>
      </Modal>

      
      <Modal
        show={show6}
        onHide={() => setShow6(false)}
        dialogClassName="modal-90w"
        aria-labelledby="example-custom-modal-styling-title"
      >
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title id="example-custom-modal-styling-title">
            Tips
          </Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
          <Tips />
        </Modal.Body>
      </Modal>

    </>
  );
};

export default BottomSection;
